OL,3,CVolunteers' #100,000 home makeover for
OL,4,Cblind girl with rare disease
OL,6,FVolunteer tradesmen have carried out a
OL,7,F#100,000 home renovation to help a
OL,8,Fblind girl with an incurable disease
OL,9,Flive more comfortably.
OL,11,FFourteen-year-old Stevie Taylor, from
OL,12,FRotherham, was diagnosed with at the
OL,13,Fage of eight, after teachers noticed
OL,14,Fshe was struggling to see in class.
OL,16,FThe degenerative condition can lead to
OL,17,Fseizures, blindness and childhood
OL,18,Fdementia.
