OL,3,CVolunteers' #100,000 home makeover for
OL,4,Cblind girl with rare disease
OL,6,FStevie's father, Paul, started trying
OL,7,Fto create a home able to meet his
OL,8,Fdaughter's long-term needs two years
OL,9,Fago, but costs quickly spiralled.
OL,11,FAfter hearing their story, the
OL,12,Fcommunity rallied around to make the
OL,13,Fproperty in Wath upon Dearne more safe
OL,14,Fand accessible.
OL,16,FMr Taylor told ITV News: "I can't
OL,17,Fthank everyone enough. I've lived here
OL,18,Fall my life and it's a place where
OL,19,Fpeople look out for each other.
