OL,6,F"All these things have been achieved
OL,7,Fbecause of what people have done for
OL,8,Fus. You can't put that into words. You
OL,9,Fcan't measure it."
OL,11,FAround 40 tradespeople inspired by
OL,12,FStevie's story stepped in, donating
OL,13,Ftime and materials which Paul believes
OL,14,Fhas saved the family at least #100,000.
OL,16,FMr Taylor said: "I always worried at
OL,17,Fnight if I heard her get up for the
OL,18,Ftoilet that she was going to turn the
OL,19,Fwrong way and fall down the stairs.
