OL,3,CVolunteers' #100,000 home makeover for
OL,4,Cblind girl with rare disease
OL,6,F"To have her bed and bathroom on the
OL,7,Fsame level and somewhere we can sleep,
OL,8,Fso we can hear her in the night, has
OL,9,Fbeen a major thing. It's helped us all
OL,10,Frelax a bit more."
OL,12,FStevie, who has been described as
OL,13,F"bright" and "bubbly" by her father,
OL,14,Falso thanked the community for
OL,15,Fcreating her dream bedroom.
OL,17,FShe added: "It's nice to know people
OL,18,Fwant to help us and put time and
OL,19,Feffort into making the house look
OL,20,Fnice."
