OL,6,FWhat is Batten disease?
OL,8,FBatten disease is a group of incurable
OL,9,Fgenetic disorders. There are 13 known
OL,10,Ftypes.
OL,12,FPassed down through families, it
OL,13,Fresults from a genetic mutation.
OL,15,FThe disorder affects cells' ability to
OL,16,Fbreak down and get rid of cellular
OL,17,Fwaste, causing problems with the
OL,18,Fnervous system.
