OL,4,Cblind girl with rare disease
OL,6,FSymptoms, which can appear in
OL,7,Fchildhood and early adulthood, include
OL,8,Fseizures, vision loss and cognitive
OL,9,Fproblems.
OL,11,FHow common is Batten disease?
OL,13,FHealthcare providers estimate that
OL,14,FBatten disease affects about one in
OL,15,Fevery 25,000 babies.
OL,17,FSiblings of children with Batten
OL,18,Fdisease have a 25% chance of having
OL,19,Fthe disorder.
