OL,3,CVolunteers' #100,000 home makeover for
OL,4,Cblind girl with rare disease
OL,6,FCurrently, there is only a treatment
OL,7,Favailable for one form of Batten
OL,8,Fdisease and there is no cure.
OL,10,FLiz Brownnutt, chief executive of
OL,11,FBatten Disease Family Association,
OL,12,Fsaid: "We ned to raise more awareness
OL,13,Fboth with the general public as well
OL,14,Fas the medical profession because we
OL,15,Fneed more treatments.
OL,17,F"We really need a quicker path to
OL,18,Fdiagnosis so that more patients can
OL,19,Fget earlier access to treatments and
OL,20,Fultimately help them found a cure."
